! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|v0.1.0 |2026-05-20 |Initial release. `<$scribe>` widget with bidirectional sync of tiddler field (or sub-path inside JSON-encoded field) with state tiddler. Three ship-on type handlers: `text/plain`, `application/json`, `application/x-string-array`. Pattern inspired by Flibbles' `FieldTranscriberWidget` in tw5-graph; this is an independent reimplementation that adds sub-path-into-JSON syncing |
